## Problem
Dark mode still has old teal values that fail WCAG AA.

## Current (WRONG)
```css
--color-green: 142 71% 59%;      /* needs 130¬∞ */
--primary: 172 66% 50%;          /* needs 38% for white text contrast */
--ring: 172 66% 50%;             /* needs 38-40% */
--sidebar-primary: 172 66% 50%;  /* needs 38% */
--sidebar-ring: 172 66% 50%;
--sidebar-active-indicator: 172 66% 50%;
```

## Required changes
```css
--color-green: 130 65% 59%;
--primary: 172 66% 38%;
--ring: 172 66% 40%;
--sidebar-primary: 172 66% 38%;
--sidebar-ring: 172 66% 40%;
--sidebar-active-indicator: 172 66% 40%;
